    "body": "## Release notes\r\n\r\n**Blog post:**\r\n\r\npreview at https://our.status.im/p/f2aa0d3c-769d-498d-9623-2977fda4107b/\r\n[done, just needs some links fixed]\r\n\r\n**Playstore:**\r\n\r\n1.17.0\r\n\r\nStatus v1.17 introduces several messenger and wallet updates, including better image sharing, privacy settings for profile pictures, and customizable thumbnails for community channels. Multi-device syncing has been added for deleted chats and modified contacts, and multisig wallet gas estimation has been fixed. And things are faster.\r\n\r\n**Status public server:**\r\n\r\nStatus v1.17 released\r\nContains the following features\r\n- \"Share\" feature for images\r\n- privacy settings for profile pictures\r\n- profile pictures in push notifications\r\n- custom emoji thumbnails for community channels\r\n- multi-device sync on deleted chats and altered contacts\r\n- added RARE token\r\n- nonce can be overridden when sending transactions\r\n- multisig gas estimation compatibility fixes\r\n- legacy tx UI for networks without EIP-1559\r\n- doubled timeline post character limit\r\n\r\n**Blockfolio signal:\r\nTwitter:\r\nFacebook:**\r\n\r\n Status v1.17 is out! \r\n\r\n Profile pictures are private by default\r\n Emoji thumbnails for community channels\r\n Multi-device sync improvements\r\n Deleted messages\r\n\r\n[link to blog (link to releases also for blockfolio signal)]\r\n\r\n**Reddit:**\r\n\r\n[post blog on release\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nSource : https://discordapp.com/channels/624205794384281629/739764149516501053/901126605190070282",
